Daintree Rainforest.title: Daintree Rainforest
Daintree Rainforest.byline: The Daintree Rainforest is a tropical rainforest in the Far North of Queensland.

Daisen (Tottori).title: Daisen (Tottori)
Daisen (Tottori).byline: Daisen (大山町 Daisen-chō) is a town in Tottori Prefecture.

Daisetsuzan National Park.title: Daisetsuzan National Park
Daisetsuzan National Park.byline: Daisetsuzan National Park (大雪山国立公園 Daisetsuzan-kokuritsukōen, also pronounced Taisetsuzan) is in the mountainous center of the island of Hokkaido.
